Clawitzer theme assets:
- wallpaper.svg – default desktop (4K Clawizter artwork; source: Clawizter.svg). Set via System Settings → Backgrounds or run set-default-wallpaper.sh.
- clawitzer-colors.css – accent colors (teal, navy) for themes.
- theme/clawitzer-theme/ – optional Cinnamon accent overrides (panel/calendar).

First-run: users can launch "Set up Clawitzer Agent" from the menu to open the agent UI and configure API keys and channels.
